{"tid":1887823,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"check下自己有冇去過高危地區","createTime":"2020-02-19T21:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T20:32:14.000Z","uid":246823,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5600f73f98110640b21abc65d003c3712146634c","tid":1887823,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T21:17:39.000Z","msg":"1) 打開疫情地圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://epitrace.github.io/#/map/hongkong/coronavirus?camp=12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepitrace.github.io%2F%23%2Fmap%2Fhongkong%2Fcoronavirus%3Fcamp%3D12&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5IlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=fd7f73b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epitrace.github.io/#/map/hongkong/coronavirus?camp=12</a><br />\n<br />\n2) 按左下角圖示<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fwLHJxe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfwLHJxe.png&h=98b15825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3) 選擇「按發病日期」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h7CyQcE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh7CyQcE.png&h=7d7a5346&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4) uncheck 「顯示所有相關地點」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zt6sac1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZt6sac1.png&h=292a9d08&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5) 係右邊條bar 選擇你有出街既日期，睇下果日你有去過地圖上出現過既地方<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BhUdQdp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBhUdQdp.png&h=63d8e241&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7dabe36d04164a2284f9cc9639acd694233010c0","tid":1887823,"uid":170281,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T21:34:12.000Z","msg":"要中就中 咁既流動性 根本避唔撚到"},{"pid":"ae426be64864a7e91e90f9c9a3db4154fa61654f","tid":1887823,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dabe36d04164a2284f9cc9639acd694233010c0","tid":1887823,"uid":170281,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T21:34:12.000Z","msg":"要中就中 咁既流動性 根本避唔撚到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T21:41:19.000Z","msg":"比自己知道有大唔大機會中<br />\n如果發現自己有病徵，可以睇下有冇去過高危地區"},{"pid":"832ca769dcd81486ff332ddca4a4f288bf92eba0","tid":1887823,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T09:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7cd75a666ac0614f804f66134a0f7a3a94fc441","tid":1887823,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T09:18:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85718147e5790d65832ec7ff792450e00a326829","tid":1887823,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:37:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484e574dd0cb4ad4add1c75813753ac70154507b","tid":1887823,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T12:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6966704307db2de76f1c49de95d282ef04482562","tid":1887823,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T12:56:51.000Z","msg":"中咗當刷首抽"},{"pid":"0ea153ec9f752751430524b4dfc71b2c9cb55be0","tid":1887823,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe9568aeacd26cebf28cbf0fa58e2f3a68e9547","tid":1887823,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ae9d0e34ed40af62832b551ab5233c9e377d96","tid":1887823,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40f139cc30a0ed0e4fbabab111f566fb3e7ca98","tid":1887823,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f06e0208c43930c6fa4e8d2a30b46988abe527","tid":1887823,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:56:42.000Z","msg":"認真睇哂佢plz <br />\n<br />\nTerry Yeung:<br />\n新聞跑來了。「文宣平台」複製貼上，再推農場內容謀利；兩登網友群起轉發，內容被一覽無遺。<br />\n<br />\n點擊沒了，連帶的商業價值都被抹殺。有些媒體，如《蘋果》，更是走會員制。<br />\n<br />\n試問，你忽然尊重的媒體工作者，要怎樣謀生？<br />\n<br />\n半年來，愈見惡化。議題被網民壞習慣，以及網軍的無形之手操控。<br />\n<br />\n然後你說：運動靜咗好多。<br />\n<br />\n改變自己，改變習慣。<br />\n<br />\n1. 不是正統媒體的新聞，不轉發。<br />\n2. 未經Fact Check、來自內容農場的消息，不要理。<br />\n3. 很多文宣大台都是盜取內容，不轉發。<br />\n4. 只轉發原創者的內容<br />\n5. 貼報道上討論區，只取少量內容，放link鼓勵點擊（尢其文宣大台該帶頭做）。<br />\n<br />\n再重覆，目標為上，才可以拯救連登垂死的熱門。<br />\n<br />\n比方說，<br />\n1. 如果兩日後有遊行，專注推行動Post；<br />\n2. 同一議題，集中處理，不要分散；<br />\n3. 有人留言「拉」，網友不需再留言；<br />\n4. 戒除政治J女性癖，不要再討論區議員身材；<br />\n5. 未能Fact Check的事情，忍痛讓佢沉。<br />\n6. 減少用極端字眼，例如「就嚟輸」；<br />\n7. 至為重要：不 要 再 推 假 標 題<br />\n<br />\n每個手足都有責任打好呢場資訊戰，改變習慣，重奪輿論主導權，大家一定做得到。<br />\n<br />\nYoutube戰線：黃色資訊片一律Coment+Like+Share&amp;Subscribe（CLS)（share做唔到的話重要片先share)<br />\n<br />\n香港人，改變。<br />\n<br />\nP.S.如果覺得有意思，煩請分享，謝謝你。<br />\n-------------------------------------------<br />\nIG：Terry_yeung_blog<br />\nIG連結：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IMS6HI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IMS6HI&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5IlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=c6326e64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IMS6HI</a>"},{"pid":"e6945cbd961f59b59d3b41f6aff1fb7921ce778f","tid":1887823,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T19:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535627fe9fb7a2aa8d974e9f9489bfb8b5b5cf87","tid":1887823,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T20:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a900af70b6426a13b9ca9fa